posting_body: ['BluWater Apartments', '11311 19th Ave SE, Everett, WA, 98208', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 15', 'OR Text', '15', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'Lakeside Living At Its Best', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 685 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Along the shores of Silver Lake, BluWater combines the tranquility of a lakeside retreat with all the conveniences of a modern, contemporary community.', 'We offer stunning one, two and three bedroom apartment homes on spacious grounds.', 'Our homes are equipped with a fireplace, garbage disposal, patio or balcony, dishwasher, washer and dryer, outside storage, free wi-fi in our lounge, fitness center and pool area.', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly.', 'Please contact us for more information.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '84BenMVlEA5L']
